headline: International Paper Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: International Paper (NYSE: IP; LSE: IPC) today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.4625 per share for the period from October 1, 2025, to December 31, 2025, inclusive, on the common stock, par value $1.00, of the Company, payable on December 16, 2025, to holders of record at the close of business on November 14, 2025.
